  1990s and comeback in blow during the 1990s , reubens kept a low profile , dedicating himself to writing and collecting a variety of things , " everything from fake food , to lamps " , although he did do some dubbing and took small parts in films such as 1992 's buffy the vampire slayer and tim burton 's batman returns ( reubens portrayed the penguin 's father ) and 1996 's matilda and dunston checks in .

